’Ů@64e9d986c3b8e407bc1740947ec5cbd859039f54d2af674c5a4c68393af99205ÚWTitle: title: format filesize
Path: Examples
Content:
Convert the size column to KB.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> ls | format filesize kB size


```
Convert the apparent column to B.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> du | format filesize B apparent


```
Convert the size data to MB.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> 4GB | format filesize MB
4000 MB

```
’Ů@f852e21e5caefbeb54e74f92846bfbd097d87f220b96e4b11893a778faf4f224ŮyTitle: title: format filesize
Path: Notes
Content:
Decimal precision is controlled by 
``$env.config.float_precision``
.
